</li>
<li id="cite&#95;note-21"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="#cite_ref-21">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text"><i><a href="/wiki/Encyclopedia_Americana" class="mw-redirect" title="Encyclopedia Americana">Encyclopedia Americana</a></i>, 30 volumes, vol. 27, New York and Chicago, 1919, pp. 395&#8211;396.</span>
